      "title": "Sri Lanka IMF discussions ongoing, talks extended for a day: mission chief",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Sri Lanka IMF discussions have been extended for one day and are still ongoing, Mission Chief Peter Bruer said in a statement.",
        "\u201cThe IMF Mission in Colombo has been extended by one day because discussions are still ongoing with the authorities,\u201d said in a statement.",
        "\u201cWe plan to conclude the mission and issue a press release on Thursday, September 1st.\u201d",
        "Sri Lanka is trying to reach a staff-level agreement with the IMF to negotiate with creditors."
      ],
